API Command

== common API command
* send swing [magnitude(int)]
        send swing magnitudes (linear interger)
* req total swing 
        request to push total swing magnitudes (linear interger)
* send msg [message(string)]
        send messages like as chat

== TRIGGER
* push swing [magnitude(int)]
        receive total swing magnitude(int)
* push msg
        receive messages
